        {
            "title": "火炭過路男遭綠色小巴撞斃 司機被捕涉未通過口腔液測試",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"火炭過路男遭綠色小巴撞斃 司機被捕涉未通過口腔液測試\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9cbec088e14a670ca9a8cec7cf5dee95/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250224/_2025022422233374150.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">火炭過路男遭綠色小巴撞斃 司機被捕涉未通過口腔液測試</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>火炭穗禾路與麗禾里交界，今日（2月24日）下午6時許發生致命車禍。一名過路男子被綠色小巴撞倒，浴血重創。救護員接報趕至，將傷者送沙田威爾斯醫院搶救，可惜回天乏術。\n\n</p>\n<p>現場所見地面遺下一道血路，警員登上小巴搜證，司機亦坐在乘客位內接受調查。現時警方已拘捕肇事司機，消息指他未能通過快速口腔液測試。目前意外原因及死者身份仍待了解。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4101403/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"肇事綠色小巴。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b0378143ca1a16bdecd4d2f8f9882144/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_211745121_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        肇事綠色小巴。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4101404/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員登上小巴調查。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/55a6eb74f4c2d98fdbac54f30a4659f9/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_211745121_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員登上小巴調查。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4101400/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉事小巴司機。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/67dc874e8064c510b5dd644ec739ab07/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_211745121_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事小巴司機。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4101401/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"地面遺下一道血路。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a3d2779ed0a619bd4257be4d9e0f63f6/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_211745121_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        地面遺下一道血路。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4101406/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f019f930a6c136a3dcfe7563fd45674e/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_211745121_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4101402/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為火炭穗禾路與麗禾里交界一過路處。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/145345fc93c70803f7a3829e420d627e/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250224_211745121_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為火炭穗禾路與麗禾里交界一過路處。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
