            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "低空經濟︱灣區專員考察珠海 指當地空域協調經驗可供參考",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"低空經濟︱灣區專員考察珠海 指當地空域協調經驗可供參考\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/896263bd4d3e38330ee43fcebe1598de/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250224/_2025022418054616369.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">低空經濟︱灣區專員考察珠海 指當地空域協調經驗可供參考</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【低空經濟/陳潔玲/粵港澳大灣區】政府致力發展低空經濟，粵港澳大灣區發展專員陳潔玲今日（24日）訪問珠海，實地考察當地低空經濟運營、綠色能源技術創新等領域的發展。陳潔玲認為，香港和珠海都是擁有多島嶼和豐富海洋資源的城市，珠海的低空空域協調及運營服務平台和常態化低空物流配送網絡建設方面的經驗，可以作為香港發展低空經濟有用的參考。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4100843/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳潔玲（中）和氣候變化專員李學賢（左二）到訪珠海，實地考察唐家港物流運營基地全國首條海島公共物流無人機配送航線的多機型、常態化運營情況。政制局fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34319cada8c0d00abc81303cf4e4bc56/2025-02/480766107_1027419325875914_2748042079417358519_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳潔玲（中）和氣候變化專員李學賢（左二）到訪珠海，實地考察唐家港物流運營基地全國首條海島公共物流無人機配送航線的多機型、常態化運營情況。政制局fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4100844/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳潔玲考察桂山島低空經濟運營中心。政制局fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/851cf3060248953bd9f55d50ed2f573a/2025-02/480916077_1027419309209249_5742276247622449478_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳潔玲考察桂山島低空經濟運營中心。政制局fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4100846/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳潔玲（右四）考察珠海市低空運營指揮中心。政制局fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fabbe2617c2229599d745a1da8165a93/2025-02/481231419_1027419389209241_1736940331295681789_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳潔玲（右四）考察珠海市低空運營指揮中心。政制局fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4100845/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"實地考察桂山海上風電場亞洲首個工業級海上風電製氫設施的運行情況。政制局fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/221956ca9395235d43e6e2f5760e84fa/2025-02/480930728_1027419302542583_2187955563239444735_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        實地考察桂山海上風電場亞洲首個工業級海上風電製氫設施的運行情況。政制局fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4100847/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"實地考察桂山海上風電場亞洲首個工業級海上風電製氫設施的運行情況。政制局fb\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a496d0c09b7ca1f90de428b7f6a33628/2025-02/481654799_1027419252542588_7638759711939657486_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        實地考察桂山海上風電場亞洲首個工業級海上風電製氫設施的運行情況。政制局fb\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>她又稱，海上風電和綠氫產業的創新結合，亦對香港在推動綠色能源發展方面有啟發作用。香港擁有「一國兩制」、內聯外通以及人才匯聚等的獨有優勢，特區政府會積極與內地方面加強溝通協作，共同探索高質量發展新路徑，為區域經濟社會發展注入新動能。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者：林彥汛\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054665/即時-港聞-低空經濟︱灣區專員考察珠海-指當地空域協調經驗可供參考",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-24 21:31:33",
