            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "劍擊｜港隊少年組累積2金1銀3銅   周二青年組繼續爭牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d6fc77d27aa88ec9d3e237f8f4ec368a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250224/_2025022421221910071.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>亞洲青少年劍擊錦標賽周一在科威特完成所有「少年組」比賽，以個人賽金牌王哲、陸浚諾、何承謙及許皓竣的少男花劍隊，在決賽以45:41擊敗中國隊，成功衛冕；可惜少年女佩在4強以一劍之微不敵中國，跟4強止步的女重團同得銅牌。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港少年花劍隊成功衛冕後，一齊豎起1字手勢，右二起 : 王哲、何承謙、陸浚諾、許皓竣。香港劍總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c0b81404768f44cd96e1455b2c0797db/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-24_at_8_30_00_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港少年花劍隊成功衛冕後，一齊豎起1字手勢，右二起 : 王哲、何承謙、陸浚諾、許皓竣。香港劍總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"男花少年隊賽前自我鼓舞一番。香港劍總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c8f69097282fe1137ce05cde27e51ed/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-24_at_8_49_27_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        男花少年隊賽前自我鼓舞一番。香港劍總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港劍總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c3e3c00108e902b5c3386c9d7610bfa6/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-24_at_8_48_15_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港劍總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港劍總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ded3f10ea9960df8c05783baf355cbd4/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-24_at_8_14_12_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港劍總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"王哲成大贏家。香港劍總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/90a3d925bd4959c53e3742f3ac38d742/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-24_at_8_48_20_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        王哲成大贏家。香港劍總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>直入16強的香港少男花劍隊，在決賽前未遇考驗，先後以45:15大勝約旦，45:21勝哈薩克及45:20勝南韓，決賽對中國，港隊從第一節已開始領先，終以45:41連續2年登頂。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"女子少年花劍隊奪得一面銅牌，港隊總教練鄭兆康亦到現場監督比賽。香港劍總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a7bb73eba0ca8a17ffd4c8fccc40ecb2/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-24_at_8_45_44_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女子少年花劍隊奪得一面銅牌，港隊總教練鄭兆康亦到現場監督比賽。香港劍總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"少年女重個人賽銀牌吳海諦。香港劍總圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d22c6c7e59269589fc9ab6c114084b3d/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-24_at_8_44_08_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        少年女重個人賽銀牌吳海諦。香港劍總圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>連同早前在個人賽的一金（男花的王哲）及一銀（女重的吳海諦），以及少年女花團體銅牌，港隊暫取竹得2金1銀3銅，周二展開青年組比賽。\n\n</p>\n<p>少年組：港隊獎牌\n\n</p>\n<p>金牌：王哲（男花少）<br/>\n金牌：男花（少年組）（王哲、陸浚諾、何承謙、許皓竣）\n\n</p>\n<p>銀牌：吳海諦（女重少）\n\n</p>\n<p>銅牌：女花團（少年組）（樊寶懿、文銥澄、龍卓盈、林曉晴）<br/>\n銅牌：女重團（少年組）（吳海諦、羅阡滺、王文雨歆、李懿穎）<br/>\n銅牌：女佩團（少年組）（曾悅澄、吳𦐒霖、鍾依廷、余傑）<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2054699/即時-體育-劍擊-港隊少年組累積2金1銀3銅-周二青年組繼續爭牌",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-24 21:31:33",
